---
layout: base.njk
title: thoughts
description: personal thoughts on security, software, ai, etc.
permalink: "/"
---

<h1 class="page-title">notes</h1>
<p class="page-intro">
  thoughts on security, software, ai, etcetera.
</p>

<div class="post-list">
  {% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
    <article class="post-list-item">
      <h2 class="post-list-title">
        <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
      </h2>

      {% if post.data.description %}
        <p class="post-list-description">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
      {% endif %}

      {% if post.date %}
        <p class="post-list-meta">{{ post.date | postDate }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </article>
  {% endfor %}
</div>